t: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;面对不断上升的开支、巨额学生债务和日益黯淡的就业前景，对一些人来说，掷骰子似乎越来越有吸引力。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/VUODiHpP6qSX1dEIQrzXeS2MSh6V_gQwD2iyUNcF2knRsUHDC57EHyqV8StV76B0kFfvPbm6WOcNKanp1OsjMdcdpRRCSguSYAjWqfDYRGLRMyCr5VreDZTLdFCJzWnKBrptoFPJpmeb_R5UtxAY9XIAOM3iGPN6FbLKtxHvM3Sinis9rGH0KB29nOhVZ4PHI1ItXhVFeoBCb868lBNvca9kgof1ILCNlw4OoLyVxCiCcBTzXvEXvlY90MBeCB7EaUNoeierDujo3G2HYwAOvkoN9elxzTcMimKvTbSlwHpEeUGX6gZfiu0skRkJ0QTlYGGAjrss-GpPK540PQQ7EgOkjWayDJ-XwJ1dCqum2ExQ20rFHQjo0nWq_cXP2iz1g-ciGH0JSQFx6Qksusy0K8oudqkgg0PNIU6RC2uFfqS2fYtelV8Mm_H4h-1f0SxBFvcB37Li8O7H5aYnMPTMlvzHlJ2fXJHSjhDU36wnNt2lw--MXMABG0bhxr-XF1BTqTOp4l1ALm7bBVQoL8pazXfZhxk/gAaxOB1O99uS8n0x6VeKjY-ySfOynO_Q/22" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;美联储&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;特朗普政府的改变可能会降低通胀数据&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;美国商务部下属的经济分析局即将对美联储首选的通胀指标进行修改，这可能会扭转今年加息的局面。花旗集团经济学家称即将进行的更新是“一件大事”。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;克里斯·布莱恩特 (Chris Bryant) 在&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;彭博社观点&lt;/em&gt;中写道，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美光科技及其韩国同行&lt;/strong&gt;面临着&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Dfb06WB7EUbOP0r5ZLa49-gmSwaFEh5aT5qbmqijOzyiMGaWCkNoHwKHLWya7Kjf5xZHWMqqDxFdWXAynVORDDLDOG1XCXb_MZcazXKG8keqKrL-18zADcvKP4ieeGsfxBTRPGTEKTgeunyHYa2e-IVBeiAai1b9WUS7tDTrDIw1fSF3W2eOOAhviJsv_1hJlpTXDcsRmd5QFXQYTMmaajBfPZSC1Z4Wxf-taBPyldhaJ0YcWrTYValMl611v8WT_LvRNaEZ1dJYgndlAsR8uhYklwDUyRrYvKYHp3fRT8mCe30wF_33F3Akou2XzzOfRwSLZ0MPxWOWC0xlFZnydjs0LIJwuzpA0FM11uIyQAxdJq6KgkzPy3AzSZz-GfcEmjFCUHjt2QjQltVzgtqKxUSmE-ye4f_Czfb_HF81fzlTcfdhNrYi1rEaSMVxu4acQwvJhn5PbHW57iTKvUnbSePXmRteC8WUqxAoLBCTmYQgMxJxsGphgBhgowae6BvG-rhkrp1DoUrh340vWG6fEtOV4piOJH4LeAvNl7whh0o6/r9STPIWjm9wgL7-IGZ2DL99ZlNkrA4uV/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="美光的巨额利润注定会带来麻烦"&gt;一个棘手的问题&lt;/a&gt;。随着人工智能数据中心耗尽存储芯片的供应， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/YF_qhYTj5B_dz6HyiIOdcI6g1434HD-v4P-6pSR2NHv1pxHB438aRCAuxJzhr4P2Tt6jJhYFOfYDJOROGVjaiuKIbQzPnO4FuQXsk0U9UlGD0SAndgH7X7SsVSPvY5gy746YMIADoCyJTHwXBSAqewRqAYqZ0Ti0ZwHbOmjOPFA6M5sFVm6gS3feqisESZQ_b9V_A3n8KDasgzslYJpVJsPsm-5buttXX6uNHLiyxDShDuoNlYJmRTy7PHLjXkgwBxyIhz97YQQ6YD3JTZKakjUaBGtMgDyFnXZK8O6MQSC7Qkj8PfoNUuLjHUWvh8SBfFrKjXcs281nN16-Ls7yW3lZ6pHKyvoxREXzBzU62yglEhYtUZ3QZFQmivVX013eARz6zWf6vvxsvBZEZ04Td4lIPx4c3yUpWhFxGn9TC0fo1GqRJ4LHmUIha0ducfNq_su75QlhBfVtEPmrvXwJC7EyPKKm1TlsPw/qj9AB8T_nxAEbjaMtFA2XYacp8cmgdnj/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="为什么人工智能的繁荣让一切变得更加昂贵"&gt;已经没有足够的&lt;/a&gt;存储芯片可供使用。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;这种稀缺性正在推高内存价格，并使美光科技、SK 海力士公司和三星电子公司盈利惊人。但客户不满意，政府可能会进行干预，短缺可能会为中国竞争对手打开大门。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/TsuNIXFgPFFE4WrubadWJZfLRuKUQN1CzY4zTw5IjsJ6sQJ5ksYhruzWo862OYwEUvYL6_UCpHriiuhIfYNlvk6EofF